# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# MyVault project additions
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Secrets & signing — this is an offline password manager. NEVER commit these.
# Encrypted vault backups the user exports (their data, even though encrypted):
*.ltvault
# Release keystores / signing material (debug.keystore is allowed above):
*.jks
*.p12
*.p8
keystore.properties
# Env / credential files (keep an .env.example if you add one):
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
google-services.json

# Build artifacts (the real outputs live under build/, but never commit a copy)
*.apk
*.aab
*.apks
*.idsig
index.android.bundle*
*.jsbundle.map

# TypeScript / lint tooling caches
*.tsbuildinfo
.eslintcache
.prettiercache

# Logs
*.log
logs/

